desc:
50% boost to all parameters of Light, Dark types, enormously boosts Light, Dark elemental damage, enormously boosts OD gauge fill rate & 10% damage reduction from Light, Dark types
Guild Raid: Boosts Atk, Def when BB gauge is over 50% & adds Extra Skill disable effects purge to UBB

dictionary.lore: A gilded medal set with amethyst and silver. It emits a faint glow reminiscent of a mystical twilight. Grants its bearer power over light and darkness.

name: Dusklight Medal
